                            <comment id="15071695" author="smilegator" created="Fri, 25 Dec 2015 18:39:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem still exists in 1.4 and 1.5, after checking the code. The code just ignores the third parameter (join type) users pass. However, the join type we called is inner, even if the user-specified type is others. Should we submit a PR for 1.4 and 1.5? &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=davies&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;davies&quot;&gt;davies&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

